title: Ep257 Amputee Crimes
description:
This week, the gals take a look at a couple of cases committed post-op. Topics include a real bummer of a hike, a bullsh** self-defense claim, and a mysterious bag of human hands. Pick up a bottle of Dunham Cellars Three-Legged Red, sharpen your pocket knife, and tune in for Amputee Crimes.

For a full list of show sponsors, visit:
